snippet.title: Midnight Fight Express Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2022
snippet.description: Humble Games brought a brand new trailer for Midnight Fight Express - an isometric brawler game taking place in a grungy city. You'll face swarms of enemies in this game written by a Co-Writer from Destiny 2. Midnight Fight Express releases August 23, 2022.
